results.name: Square array of binomial transforms of Chebyshev polynomial coefficients.
comment: Square array of binomial transforms of rows of A081277. Rows include A007051, A006234, A081278, A081279, A081280.
example: Read by antidiagonals, the array appears as {1}, {1,2},{1,4,5}, {1,6,15,14}, {1,8,29,54,41},...
